<emphasis id="2E18D0B5F8AD709D65933C2390385778" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">Oxytate bicornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Liu, Liu &amp; Xu, 2017, female. 
<emphasis id="67A8416A5FD5605A0FD7D779CD10B5B2" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">A</emphasis>
habitus, dorsal view 
